    - rid: 107151359355650139
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650140
          - rid: 107151359355650141
          output: 'The roaring flames of the theater are the only entertainment the
            commoners shall derive from that establishment. It appears the play has
            been canceled... permanently. Our men saw to that personally!

            [Gained
            10 Bliss & 10 Flock]

'
        - weight: 40
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650142
          - rid: 107151359355650143
          - rid: 107151359355650144
          output: 'Our men are successful in lighting the fires, but lamentably,
            members of the rival sect were nearby and managed to quench the blaze.
            So much organization... for naught! At the very least, our hand was not
            discovered, though the play shall now proceed as planned.

            [Gained
            10 Flock Lost 20 Zeal & 15 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 10
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650145
          - rid: 107151359355650146
          output: 'Terrible news! Our plan succeeded, but our men became trapped
            within the inferno. When the fires were extinguished and their charred
            remains were discovered, enough evidence was left intact to trace the
            deed back to us. There may be no play, but the outcome is far worse!

            [Lost
            40 Zeal & 15 Bliss]

'
